WEBVTT

01:31.080 --> 01:34.960
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.590 --> 01:36.400
Repeat the year?

01:35.789 --> 01:39.539
[2006]

01:37.039 --> 01:37.840
We can't afford

01:37.840 --> 01:39.280
to let her waste another year.

01:39.280 --> 01:40.789
She usually has good grades.

01:40.789 --> 01:42.000
If she hadn't had a fever during the exam,

01:42.000 --> 01:43.590
she would've gotten into a top university.

01:43.590 --> 01:45.479
And she'll do better if she does it again?

01:45.479 --> 01:46.479
And does graduating from a top university

01:45.670 --> 01:48.030
[University Introduction Brochure]

01:46.479 --> 01:47.680
guarantee a good job?

01:48.120 --> 01:49.479
She should apply for a normal school

01:49.479 --> 01:50.580
or a sponsored training program.

01:50.580 --> 01:52.280
She can work right after graduation.

01:52.280 --> 01:53.710
We don't expect her
to support us in our old age,

01:52.390 --> 01:55.020
[Xiangsheng 2006 General Higher Education Admissions
Candidate Preference Form]

01:54.229 --> 01:56.759
but she should at least
stop asking us for money.

01:56.759 --> 01:57.950
Keep your voice down.

01:57.950 --> 01:59.550
Don't let the child hear you.

02:03.590 --> 02:05.980
[Aosheng Normal University]

02:08.680 --> 02:10.419
[Knowledge Can Change Your Life]

02:15.100 --> 02:18.320
[Episode 4: Knowledge Can Change Your Life]

02:19.270 --> 02:19.750
How is it?

02:19.750 --> 02:20.680
Slow down, Meng.

02:22.150 --> 02:23.210
Is it from Xiaolan?

02:28.030 --> 02:28.710
Is it not?

02:32.520 --> 02:33.650
It's from Jiang Yan?

02:33.910 --> 02:35.110
So many letters at it?

02:35.240 --> 02:37.100
You two still write to each other?

02:37.750 --> 02:39.150
I don't know how to reply.

02:39.630 --> 02:41.030
She moved away years ago.

02:41.280 --> 02:42.610
I don't have much to say.

02:43.430 --> 02:45.430
Dating is such a hassle.

02:45.630 --> 02:46.710
She likes you,

02:46.970 --> 02:48.160
yet you like her.

02:49.630 --> 02:50.960
What are you laughing at?

02:50.960 --> 02:52.960
It'll happen to you sooner or later.

02:58.360 --> 02:59.240
Why are you out here

02:59.240 --> 03:00.640
during work hours again?

03:00.680 --> 03:02.430
The job Second Uncle got me

03:02.430 --> 03:03.590
is just for show.

03:03.630 --> 03:05.000
It makes no difference

03:05.020 --> 03:06.360
whether I'm there or not.

03:06.360 --> 03:07.820
Your workplace is better.

03:08.520 --> 03:09.120
By the way,

03:09.190 --> 03:09.800
are you going to

03:09.800 --> 03:11.260
report for duty next week?

03:12.360 --> 03:13.960
I haven't decided if I'm going.

03:13.960 --> 03:15.120
What's there to think about?

03:15.120 --> 03:16.470
Isn't that what life is?

03:16.470 --> 03:17.750
School, work,

03:18.030 --> 03:19.000
marriage, kids.

03:19.520 --> 03:20.590
Now that high school is over,

03:20.590 --> 03:21.590
it's time to work.

03:22.030 --> 03:23.560
It's the same for everyone.

03:26.870 --> 03:28.530
If it's the same for everyone,

03:29.750 --> 03:31.590
does it mean I have to be the same too?

03:31.590 --> 03:32.750
What else can you do?

03:33.030 --> 03:34.560
At most, we can sneak around

03:34.870 --> 03:36.530
doing some business like now.

03:37.150 --> 03:38.680
When are we going next time?

03:40.120 --> 03:41.120
I was thinking of

03:41.400 --> 03:43.030
going to Anqing again next week

03:43.030 --> 03:44.430
to wrap up that business.

03:45.150 --> 03:46.280
Reselling cigarettes

03:46.280 --> 03:47.470
doesn't violate regulations,

03:47.470 --> 03:48.710
but it's exploiting a loophole.

03:48.710 --> 03:49.800
It's not a long-term solution.

03:49.800 --> 03:50.280
Yeah.

03:50.470 --> 03:52.270
It's really profitable though.

03:52.310 --> 03:53.360
Anyway, I'll listen to you,

03:53.360 --> 03:53.840
Cheng.

03:54.560 --> 03:55.490
Let's go. Get in.

04:11.710 --> 04:12.400
Chen Qing?

04:12.560 --> 04:13.490
Why are you here?

04:13.630 --> 04:14.360
Um, these are

04:14.560 --> 04:16.120
some high school textbooks.

04:16.120 --> 04:16.779
Take a look.

04:17.070 --> 04:17.680
Thank you.

04:19.390 --> 04:20.560
I asked about the school

04:20.560 --> 04:21.269
for you.

04:21.560 --> 04:22.630
No.1 High School

04:22.630 --> 04:24.120
is accepting transfer students now.

04:24.120 --> 04:25.920
But since you only have
a middle school diploma,

04:25.920 --> 04:27.800
you have to take an exam first.

04:28.190 --> 04:29.390
If your score meets

04:29.390 --> 04:30.630
last year's associate degree cutoff,

04:30.630 --> 04:32.090
they'll let you transfer.

04:32.240 --> 04:33.300
But the problem is,

04:33.630 --> 04:34.560
English has been added

04:34.560 --> 04:35.510
to the total score this year,

04:35.510 --> 04:36.840
so it might be harder...

04:36.920 --> 04:37.750
Then what was the cutoff

04:37.750 --> 04:39.240
for science associate degrees last year?

04:39.240 --> 04:40.240
Science degrees?

04:40.720 --> 04:42.720
The total score for science was 690.

04:42.920 --> 04:45.000
And the associate degree cutoff was 350.

04:45.000 --> 04:46.430
You want to study science?

04:46.430 --> 04:46.830
Xiaolan,

04:46.830 --> 04:48.360
I suggest you choose liberal arts.

04:48.360 --> 04:49.580
If it's liberal arts, I can...

04:49.580 --> 04:50.000
So,

04:50.120 --> 04:51.580
when is the transfer exam?

04:52.159 --> 04:53.040
Next Monday.

04:53.800 --> 04:55.400
That's less than a week away.

04:55.650 --> 04:56.909
It's going to be tough.

04:57.600 --> 04:58.200
Thank you.

04:59.040 --> 05:00.720
L-L-Let me help you push the bike.

05:00.720 --> 05:01.600
No need.

05:01.630 --> 05:02.230
It's okay.

05:02.480 --> 05:03.210
Here, let me.

05:03.480 --> 05:04.540
You hold the books.

05:04.560 --> 05:05.160
Thank you.

05:05.830 --> 05:07.330
I was a science student originally.

05:07.330 --> 05:10.130
Switching to liberal arts now
would be a disaster.

05:14.040 --> 05:15.310
I'll get going then.

05:15.830 --> 05:16.630
Okay, thanks.

05:25.240 --> 05:25.800
Xiaolan.

05:26.870 --> 05:27.600
Chen Qing brought you

05:27.600 --> 05:28.560
so many books?

05:29.750 --> 05:30.800
Chen Qing prepared

05:30.800 --> 05:32.460
these study materials for me.

05:32.770 --> 05:33.560
I plan to go take

05:33.560 --> 05:35.190
No.1 High School's exam on Monday.

05:35.190 --> 05:35.800
Xiaolan,

05:36.070 --> 05:37.800
you are really going to take it?

05:39.390 --> 05:40.630
I remember before,

05:40.630 --> 05:41.720
when you were in middle school,

05:41.720 --> 05:43.000
your mom asked
if you wanted to go to high school,

05:43.000 --> 05:44.040
and you said no.

05:44.040 --> 05:45.900
Why do you want to study again now?

05:47.600 --> 05:49.060
Doesn't it say on the wall?

05:49.480 --> 05:50.950
"Knowledge can change your life."

05:50.950 --> 05:52.159
I think it's right.

05:52.680 --> 05:53.630
And I think

05:53.630 --> 05:55.430
I need an urban household registration.

05:55.430 --> 05:56.720
Doesn't getting into college

05:56.720 --> 05:59.250
guarantee an urban household registration?

05:59.720 --> 06:00.240
Yes.

06:00.720 --> 06:02.780
Studying is definitely a good thing.

06:04.360 --> 06:05.430
But getting into college

06:05.430 --> 06:06.720
isn't that simple.

06:07.240 --> 06:09.190
We don't need to compete

06:09.190 --> 06:10.630
with Xia Ziyu on studying.

06:10.630 --> 06:12.560
We're better than her in many other ways.

06:12.560 --> 06:13.950
I think it's good

06:13.950 --> 06:15.390
that Xiaolan wants to go to college.

06:15.390 --> 06:16.730
Let the Xia family see

06:17.120 --> 06:18.270
how blind they are.

06:18.870 --> 06:20.510
Well, it's certainly good if she gets in.

06:20.510 --> 06:21.970
She'll definitely get in.

06:22.720 --> 06:24.250
Leave the fried cakes to me.

06:24.560 --> 06:26.090
You just focus on studying.

06:27.670 --> 06:29.400
Comrade Liu Fen,

06:29.560 --> 06:31.310
don't get ahead of yourself.

06:31.310 --> 06:32.640
Nothing is certain yet.

06:32.920 --> 06:34.180
I'm going to study now.

06:41.750 --> 06:42.560
If I'm lucky,

06:42.630 --> 06:44.950
I can take next year's
college entrance exam.

06:44.950 --> 06:46.070
English, which might be difficult

06:46.070 --> 06:47.240
for many test-takers now,

06:47.240 --> 06:48.430
is my strength.

06:49.750 --> 06:50.560
All these years

06:50.560 --> 06:52.040
of working in foreign trade sales

06:52.040 --> 06:53.170
wasn't for nothing.

06:54.830 --> 06:56.480
"Knowledge can change your life."

06:56.480 --> 06:58.810
I'll trust this one more time
in this life.

07:09.630 --> 07:10.480
Smells good, doesn't it?

07:10.480 --> 07:11.560
Don't rush.

07:11.750 --> 07:12.610
It's all yours.

07:13.480 --> 07:14.480
Where's the bike?

07:15.750 --> 07:16.360
Xiaolan.

07:18.560 --> 07:19.120
The bike?

07:19.560 --> 07:21.220
Your uncle lent it to someone.

07:21.270 --> 07:22.000
For now,

07:22.160 --> 07:23.560
just stay home and revise.

07:23.560 --> 07:24.870
Don't do any chores.

07:24.950 --> 07:25.830
Go read your books.

07:25.830 --> 07:27.560
We've got things covered here.

08:07.630 --> 08:08.830
Xiaolan is studying.

08:08.870 --> 08:09.340
Get down!

08:09.340 --> 08:09.870
Get down!

08:11.830 --> 08:13.160
Did you hear what Mom said?

08:13.160 --> 08:13.890
Keep it down.

08:16.560 --> 08:18.070
Mom, what's for dinner?

08:18.480 --> 08:20.140
All you think about is eating.

08:21.120 --> 08:22.830
Here comes the fish.

08:24.240 --> 08:24.830
Come on.

08:25.190 --> 08:25.720
Xiaolan,

08:26.000 --> 08:26.860
have some fish.

08:27.190 --> 08:28.310
It helps with studying.

08:28.310 --> 08:29.310
Eat more chicken.

08:29.480 --> 08:31.340
Winner, winner, chicken dinner.

08:34.669 --> 08:35.870
Xiaolan, you eat too.

08:36.270 --> 08:37.200
Good boy.

08:37.240 --> 08:38.100
Thank you, Tao.

09:04.630 --> 09:05.290
Don't grab.

09:07.150 --> 09:08.550
You just want to eat it all yourself?

09:08.550 --> 09:09.600
Leaving so early?

09:12.480 --> 09:13.080
Xiaolan,

09:13.150 --> 09:15.030
you sure know how to dress.

09:15.750 --> 09:16.360
It looks

09:16.790 --> 09:17.720
really good!

09:17.960 --> 09:18.550
She's smart.

09:18.550 --> 09:19.750
Smart at everything.

09:19.870 --> 09:20.870
Smart at dressing,

09:20.870 --> 09:21.910
and smart at studying.

09:21.910 --> 09:23.360
-Xiaolan.
-You should wear it when it's cold.

09:23.360 --> 09:24.200
Don't catch a cold.

09:24.200 --> 09:25.000
Take two eggs.

09:27.200 --> 09:28.150
Got everything?

09:28.390 --> 09:29.390
Don't be nervous.

09:30.120 --> 09:31.030
Wait for my good news.

09:31.030 --> 09:31.490
I'm off.

09:31.870 --> 09:32.720
I'll give you a ride.

09:32.720 --> 09:33.320
No need!

09:33.550 --> 09:34.010
I'm off!

09:36.720 --> 09:37.250
Xiaolan,

09:37.480 --> 09:38.740
don't feel pressured.

09:38.910 --> 09:40.640
It's no shame if you don't pass!

09:41.200 --> 09:42.330
What are you saying?

09:43.120 --> 09:44.380
I think she'll be fine.

09:45.030 --> 09:47.200
It's been so long
since she touched a textbook.

09:47.200 --> 09:48.860
She's only revised for a week.

09:49.160 --> 09:50.560
It's normal if she fails.

09:53.360 --> 09:55.930
[Anqing No. 1 High School]

09:56.000 --> 09:58.000
[Teacher's Office]

10:08.200 --> 10:09.030
Xia Xiaolan,

10:09.390 --> 10:10.990
you can start answering now.

10:15.840 --> 10:17.440
Phonetic differentiation.

10:17.910 --> 10:19.320
Find the vowel sound

10:19.320 --> 10:20.380
that is different.

10:22.270 --> 10:23.870
These questions are so kind.

10:24.080 --> 10:25.880
Are they really not free points?

10:54.360 --> 10:55.320
Ma'am, I'm done.

10:59.080 --> 10:59.560
Here.

11:02.790 --> 11:03.270
Ma'am,

11:03.270 --> 11:04.870
when will the results be out?

11:05.790 --> 11:06.850
In just a day or two.

11:06.910 --> 11:08.000
If you pass, I'll have Chen Qing

11:08.000 --> 11:09.080
pass on the message.

11:09.080 --> 11:10.410
Okay. Thank you, Ma'am.

11:14.440 --> 11:15.770
The exam questions these days

11:15.770 --> 11:16.440
are simpler

11:16.440 --> 11:18.840
than what I took for
the National College Entrance Examination.

11:18.840 --> 11:20.440
English is very basic.

11:20.630 --> 11:21.960
Math isn't hard either.

11:22.080 --> 11:23.630
I wasn't a bad student to begin with.

11:23.630 --> 11:25.320
Plus, with a body of this age,

11:25.520 --> 11:27.320
my memory seems pretty good too.

11:28.440 --> 11:30.080
God sent me back to 1983

11:30.390 --> 11:32.000
maybe to give me a real chance

11:32.690 --> 11:34.150
to become a winner in life.

11:47.960 --> 11:48.600
Xia!

11:48.870 --> 11:49.440
Xia.

11:49.720 --> 11:50.520
What's wrong?

11:52.240 --> 11:53.670
W-Why is she here?

11:56.320 --> 11:58.450
She walked out of No.1 High School too.

12:00.390 --> 12:00.870
Oh no.

12:01.440 --> 12:03.700
Is she really trying to get into college?

12:06.960 --> 12:07.630
What are you doing?

12:07.630 --> 12:09.330
I'm going to send a telegram to Ziyu!

12:09.330 --> 12:11.190
I can't count on you for anything.

12:25.320 --> 12:25.750
Fen.

12:26.320 --> 12:26.750
Fen.

12:27.240 --> 12:28.120
Stop standing there.

12:28.120 --> 12:29.030
You've been standing for 2 hours.

12:29.030 --> 12:30.120
Aren't you tired?

12:34.000 --> 12:34.720
Come on.

12:35.360 --> 12:37.360
Xiaolan will be back after the exam.

12:37.550 --> 12:39.150
It's tiring standing there.

12:39.360 --> 12:40.090
Just sit down

12:40.220 --> 12:41.670
and have some sunflower seeds.

12:41.670 --> 12:42.240
Mom!

12:43.150 --> 12:43.720
I'm back.

12:45.120 --> 12:46.150
Xiaolan is back.

12:47.200 --> 12:47.660
Auntie,

12:48.000 --> 12:48.870
I picked out

12:48.870 --> 12:49.840
some new fabric for you.

12:49.840 --> 12:51.000
Stop wearing gray and blue all the time.

12:51.000 --> 12:52.670
Try these bright stripes.

12:52.690 --> 12:53.720
They'll look great as new clothes.

12:53.720 --> 12:54.360
Okay, thank you.

12:54.360 --> 12:55.360
Drink some water.

12:55.480 --> 12:56.340
Thanks, Uncle.

13:02.150 --> 13:03.280
You must be thirsty.

13:03.710 --> 13:04.240
Thirsty.

13:05.750 --> 13:06.950
I'll go inside first.

13:08.510 --> 13:09.200
Xiaolan.

13:09.440 --> 13:10.840
How did you do on the exam?

13:12.790 --> 13:13.390
This kid!

13:13.410 --> 13:14.760
Why are you everywhere?

13:15.800 --> 13:16.330
Xiaolan.

13:16.510 --> 13:17.600
The exam is over.

13:17.670 --> 13:18.870
Let's not dwell on it.

13:19.270 --> 13:19.720
Right.

13:20.080 --> 13:21.200
We talked it over.

13:21.390 --> 13:22.790
We support you going to college.

13:22.790 --> 13:23.390
If it doesn't work out,

13:23.390 --> 13:24.750
start over
from the first year of high school.

13:24.750 --> 13:25.630
Study for 3 years,

13:25.630 --> 13:26.870
and you'll definitely pass
the college entrance exam next time.

13:26.870 --> 13:27.630
Right, right.

13:27.630 --> 13:29.080
It doesn't matter
if it's a bachelor's degree or not.

13:29.080 --> 13:30.480
For our family, even an associate degree

13:30.480 --> 13:31.670
would be a huge blessing.

13:31.670 --> 13:32.030
Right?

13:32.030 --> 13:32.670
Exactly.

13:32.840 --> 13:33.630
As for the money,

13:33.630 --> 13:34.750
you don't need to worry.

13:34.750 --> 13:36.240
I'll go out to work right away

13:36.240 --> 13:37.390
to pay for your college.

13:37.390 --> 13:37.750
I-I

13:37.750 --> 13:40.210
can also earn money
to support your studies.

13:41.910 --> 13:43.840
Thank you, Uncle, Auntie, and Mom.

13:44.080 --> 13:44.670
But I think

13:44.670 --> 13:45.750
I did pretty well.

13:46.320 --> 13:47.710
Maybe you should prepare

13:47.710 --> 13:49.840
for me to take the college entrance exam
next year.

13:49.840 --> 13:51.470
When will the results be out?

13:51.600 --> 13:52.870
In a day or two.

13:53.080 --> 13:54.000
Did you hear that?

13:54.000 --> 13:55.130
She did pretty well.

13:56.320 --> 13:56.830
Dad.

13:57.120 --> 13:58.870
What score is "pretty well"?

13:59.240 --> 14:00.750
We'll know in a couple of days.

14:00.750 --> 14:01.590
Go get dinner ready.

14:01.590 --> 14:02.160
Right.

14:16.120 --> 14:16.720
Ms. Qi,

14:17.600 --> 14:19.130
a parent is looking for you.

14:19.270 --> 14:20.200
Okay, I'll be right there.

14:20.200 --> 14:20.600
Okay.

14:28.000 --> 14:28.720
Here, try it.

14:28.720 --> 14:29.450
Is it too hot?

14:29.790 --> 14:30.390
All right.

14:33.870 --> 14:35.000
Liang has been

14:35.030 --> 14:36.000
rushing me

14:36.150 --> 14:37.240
to go work with him.

14:38.150 --> 14:39.270
The family needs money

14:39.270 --> 14:40.200
right now, too.

14:41.150 --> 14:42.790
So I quickly renewed
the contract with him.

14:42.790 --> 14:43.670
You have to take care

14:43.670 --> 14:45.000
of yourself out there.

14:45.510 --> 14:47.120
Don't worry. I've got things covered here.

14:47.120 --> 14:48.580
I'll take good care of Tao.

14:48.750 --> 14:49.600
As for Fen and Xiaolan,

14:49.600 --> 14:50.390
I won't let them

14:50.390 --> 14:51.600
be mistreated either.

14:51.600 --> 14:52.480
It's going to be

14:53.150 --> 14:54.280
hard on you, though.

14:54.840 --> 14:56.080
It won't wear me out.

14:56.790 --> 14:58.650
Look how sensible Xiaolan is now.

14:58.870 --> 14:59.390
She also

14:59.430 --> 15:00.860
has what she wants to do

15:01.320 --> 15:02.980
in the future all figured out.

15:03.870 --> 15:04.600
That's true.

15:05.200 --> 15:06.360
After going through that ordeal,

15:06.360 --> 15:08.560
it's like she's suddenly enlightened.

15:08.600 --> 15:09.800
Anyway, whether it's

15:10.030 --> 15:10.960
studying

15:11.120 --> 15:12.180
or doing business,

15:12.360 --> 15:13.820
they are all honest paths.

15:13.870 --> 15:15.030
As her elders,

15:15.270 --> 15:16.030
we have to support her.

15:16.030 --> 15:16.630
Of course.

15:16.630 --> 15:17.760
We must support her.

15:18.200 --> 15:18.840
How is it?

15:19.080 --> 15:19.960
Does it feel good?

15:19.960 --> 15:20.750
It does.

15:22.870 --> 15:23.600
Give me a kiss.

15:23.600 --> 15:24.870
Hey!

15:24.890 --> 15:26.250
Just give me a kiss.

15:29.550 --> 15:30.120
Fengmei!

15:30.360 --> 15:31.290
I'm heading out!

15:33.510 --> 15:34.080
Uncle!

15:35.080 --> 15:36.080
Are you going out?

15:36.360 --> 15:37.560
I'm going out to work.

15:37.630 --> 15:39.030
I need to buy some things.

15:39.750 --> 15:40.750
I'll go with you.

15:42.600 --> 15:43.400
Let's go then.

15:48.000 --> 15:49.080
You insist on coming with me

15:49.080 --> 15:50.670
because you have something to say to me?

15:50.670 --> 15:51.910
I have a question for you.

15:51.910 --> 15:52.480
Ask away.

15:52.750 --> 15:54.030
No need to be so mysterious.

15:54.030 --> 15:55.360
I'll ask directly then.

15:56.840 --> 15:57.360
Uncle,

15:57.960 --> 15:59.560
are you really a bricklayer?

15:59.600 --> 16:01.330
You aren't smuggling, are you?

16:03.270 --> 16:05.270
What nonsense are you talking about?

16:05.270 --> 16:07.000
You shouldn't joke about that.

16:08.240 --> 16:09.550
The other day, Chen Qing said

16:09.550 --> 16:10.600
there was a call for you.

16:10.600 --> 16:12.120
You looked nervous.

16:12.390 --> 16:13.790
I felt something was wrong.

16:13.790 --> 16:15.200
And before, you warned me

16:15.200 --> 16:17.200
that Zhou Cheng might be a smuggler.

16:17.320 --> 16:18.180
I was thinking,

16:18.440 --> 16:20.170
if you hadn't done it yourself,

16:20.440 --> 16:21.900
how would you know so much?

16:22.600 --> 16:24.090
I asked Auntie.

16:24.320 --> 16:25.600
Your income as a bricklayer

16:25.600 --> 16:26.750
is too impressive.

16:27.080 --> 16:28.360
Take this bicycle.

16:28.750 --> 16:30.150
It must cost at least 200.

16:30.240 --> 16:31.390
What kind of bricklayer

16:31.390 --> 16:33.080
can afford a bike in 6 months?

16:33.440 --> 16:34.580
I was just guessing,

16:35.000 --> 16:36.460
but seeing your reaction,

16:37.550 --> 16:38.720
I'm probably right.

16:40.600 --> 16:41.270
Xiaolan.

16:41.600 --> 16:43.120
I really am a bricklayer.

16:43.960 --> 16:45.120
It's just that sometimes,

16:45.120 --> 16:45.630
they ask me

16:45.630 --> 16:47.030
to watch over some goods.

16:47.270 --> 16:48.070
But I promise,

16:48.200 --> 16:49.120
I never asked

16:49.120 --> 16:50.250
what the goods were.

16:51.240 --> 16:51.840
Of course.

16:53.440 --> 16:54.270
I believe you.

16:54.910 --> 16:55.670
But business with unknown sources

16:55.670 --> 16:56.930
that makes quick money

16:57.270 --> 16:58.360
is usually dangerous.

16:58.360 --> 16:58.790
Yes.

16:59.200 --> 17:00.720
Making money is important,

17:00.720 --> 17:01.790
but you have to think about your family.

17:01.790 --> 17:02.270
Right?

17:02.550 --> 17:02.960
Yes.

17:03.390 --> 17:04.550
S-So I...

17:04.680 --> 17:05.960
turned down the job

17:05.960 --> 17:07.160
on the phone that day.

17:07.200 --> 17:08.349
Th-This time I really am

17:08.349 --> 17:10.010
going to work as a bricklayer.

17:11.829 --> 17:12.560
Then, Uncle,

17:13.270 --> 17:14.240
what if I said

17:14.400 --> 17:16.069
I have a business that makes money faster,

17:16.069 --> 17:17.550
and I want to partner with you?

17:17.550 --> 17:18.410
Do you trust me?

17:20.349 --> 17:21.349
What business?

17:22.680 --> 17:24.010
I want to go to Longcheng

17:24.109 --> 17:25.040
to sell clothes.

17:25.960 --> 17:27.720
But you're still in school.

17:27.750 --> 17:29.080
How can you do business?

17:29.750 --> 17:30.310
It's precisely because

17:30.310 --> 17:31.840
I want to focus on my studies

17:31.960 --> 17:33.240
that I need an easier,

17:33.240 --> 17:34.640
more profitable business.

17:34.640 --> 17:36.240
When I need to study for exams,

17:36.240 --> 17:38.040
I'll hand the business to my mom.

17:39.510 --> 17:40.270
I know.

17:40.680 --> 17:42.750
You wouldn't let me
go without money for school.

17:42.750 --> 17:44.160
But I'm an adult now.

17:44.400 --> 17:46.000
I should take care of myself.

17:46.350 --> 17:46.830
Uncle,

17:47.110 --> 17:48.640
you understand, don't you?

17:53.510 --> 17:55.110
Actually, over these years,

17:55.440 --> 17:56.550
I've been out and about,

17:56.550 --> 17:58.070
and seen a bit of the world.

17:58.640 --> 18:00.270
The clothing business is doable.

18:00.270 --> 18:01.720
I just don't have the eye for it,

18:01.720 --> 18:03.250
so I never thought about it.

18:03.480 --> 18:05.340
But Xiaolan, I think you can do it.

18:05.680 --> 18:06.680
These days, I feel

18:06.680 --> 18:07.960
that your vision

18:08.110 --> 18:09.680
seems to be ahead of mine.

18:10.720 --> 18:13.050
So if you want to do
the clothing business,

18:13.160 --> 18:14.090
I believe in you.

18:14.720 --> 18:15.590
Thank you, Uncle!

18:15.590 --> 18:17.390
I'll go buy the train ticket now.

18:18.750 --> 18:19.680
Without a letter of introduction,

18:19.680 --> 18:21.480
how are you going to buy a ticket?

18:22.830 --> 18:24.290
A letter of introduction?

18:29.930 --> 18:30.560
Xiaolan.

18:35.000 --> 18:35.440
Look.

18:36.790 --> 18:38.850
I got you the letter of introduction.

18:39.440 --> 18:40.880
I had to ask several people
in Dahe Village

18:40.880 --> 18:42.270
to get it done.

18:42.790 --> 18:44.110
So I was thinking,

18:44.310 --> 18:45.200
we need to transfer

18:45.200 --> 18:47.680
you and your mother's family register
back here as soon as possible.

18:47.680 --> 18:48.680
Thank you, Uncle.

18:50.270 --> 18:51.880
I have to go out to work.

18:52.720 --> 18:53.550
As for Longcheng,

18:53.550 --> 18:55.210
you'll have to go by yourself.

18:55.440 --> 18:56.310
Be careful.

18:56.750 --> 18:57.960
Don't worry, Uncle.

18:58.200 --> 18:59.030
I've been doing business

18:59.030 --> 19:00.030
on my own for so long.

19:00.030 --> 19:01.230
Don't worry about it.

19:02.070 --> 19:02.550
Okay.

19:05.590 --> 19:06.830
These life details

19:06.830 --> 19:07.750
of the 80s,

19:08.480 --> 19:10.080
if Uncle hadn't reminded me,

19:10.160 --> 19:11.820
I really wouldn't have known.

19:12.580 --> 19:13.190
Cheng,

19:13.270 --> 19:14.570
we'll arrive tomorrow.

19:14.570 --> 19:15.700
Why send a telegram?

19:17.200 --> 19:18.030
I have a hunch.

19:19.030 --> 19:19.550
Although we haven't

19:19.550 --> 19:20.610
been away for long,

19:21.050 --> 19:22.400
Comrade Xiaolan's progress

19:22.400 --> 19:24.660
might be changing with each passing day.

19:24.790 --> 19:25.350
If I don't

19:25.350 --> 19:26.880
tell her in advance this time,

19:26.880 --> 19:28.140
we might not even meet.

19:28.240 --> 19:28.510
Let's go.

19:28.510 --> 19:28.960
Okay.

19:29.640 --> 19:30.300
I'll drive.

19:30.750 --> 19:31.350
You drive.

19:35.680 --> 19:36.310
Fengmei.

19:36.830 --> 19:37.760
My brother left?

19:38.240 --> 19:39.770
He left early in the morning

19:39.830 --> 19:40.720
in a rush.

19:42.070 --> 19:43.530
I picked some vegetables.

19:43.550 --> 19:45.070
He should have eaten before leaving.

19:45.070 --> 19:45.870
It's his loss.

19:45.960 --> 19:47.420
We'll eat them ourselves.

19:47.440 --> 19:48.030
Mom!

19:48.720 --> 19:49.680
Mom, Auntie!

19:50.400 --> 19:50.960
Xiaolan.

19:51.750 --> 19:53.880
I've already bought the train ticket.

19:56.110 --> 19:56.840
Xia Xiaolan!

19:57.270 --> 19:57.870
Telegram!

19:59.110 --> 19:59.830
Chen Hongwei!

19:59.830 --> 20:00.400
That's me.

20:00.400 --> 20:00.790
Here.

20:01.240 --> 20:02.110
Wang Zhenzhen.

20:02.310 --> 20:03.000
Mine, mine.

20:03.550 --> 20:04.480
I'm Xia Xiaolan.

20:04.590 --> 20:05.720
Xia Xiaolan, right?

20:06.110 --> 20:07.480
Yours is a telegram.

20:07.640 --> 20:08.590
-A telegram?
-Five of them.

20:08.590 --> 20:09.250
Take a look.

20:10.200 --> 20:11.640
Sign here if everything is fine.

20:11.640 --> 20:13.790
Dayong's family
must have rich relatives in the city.

20:13.790 --> 20:14.720
That's such a thick telegram.

20:14.720 --> 20:16.200
Those are charged by the character.

20:16.200 --> 20:17.530
How much must that cost?

20:17.750 --> 20:18.320
Actually,

20:18.320 --> 20:19.240
if it's nothing urgent,

20:19.240 --> 20:20.440
writing a letter would be enough.

20:20.440 --> 20:20.960
We can

20:21.120 --> 20:22.440
deliver letters here too.

20:22.440 --> 20:23.160
Okay, thank you.

20:23.160 --> 20:23.550
Okay.

20:23.750 --> 20:24.240
Say,

20:24.240 --> 20:25.770
is there a boy who likes her?

20:26.240 --> 20:26.720
No.

20:27.070 --> 20:27.600
Let's go.

20:28.000 --> 20:28.480
Fen.

20:29.220 --> 20:31.150
You're her mother. You have to ask.

20:32.830 --> 20:33.790
Hello, Xiaolan,

20:34.160 --> 20:35.620
Since we parted last time,

20:35.640 --> 20:36.350
although I have long wanted

20:36.350 --> 20:38.200
to come to Anqing to visit you again,

20:38.200 --> 20:40.440
I was tied down
by trivial matters in the capital.

20:40.440 --> 20:41.590
I missed you so much.

20:42.480 --> 20:44.000
I wonder if you

20:44.000 --> 20:45.110
feel the same way.

20:47.270 --> 20:48.750
When you see this letter,

20:49.790 --> 20:51.070
I will have already left the capital

20:51.070 --> 20:51.790
for Anqing.

20:52.590 --> 20:54.050
I should arrive tomorrow.

20:54.590 --> 20:56.750
I will still be staying at the guesthouse.

20:56.750 --> 20:58.750
I hope to see you.

21:02.000 --> 21:02.440
Here.

21:03.680 --> 21:04.210
Xiaolan.

21:05.720 --> 21:06.650
How does it look?

21:07.590 --> 21:08.030
Mom,

21:08.400 --> 21:09.200
what is this?

21:10.440 --> 21:11.720
To hold money.

21:12.480 --> 21:13.920
This is so safe.

21:14.960 --> 21:15.510
Mom!

21:17.400 --> 21:18.440
Ten yuan a note—

21:18.680 --> 21:19.790
six hundred yuan is a thick stack.

21:19.790 --> 21:21.250
Do you think it fits there?

21:22.750 --> 21:23.590
Let me try.

21:27.510 --> 21:28.640
It is a bit too small.

21:29.160 --> 21:29.760
Hold this.

21:30.590 --> 21:31.440
I'll sew a bigger one

21:31.440 --> 21:32.370
right next to it.

21:32.470 --> 21:32.920
Mom!

21:34.680 --> 21:36.280
Why don't you separate them?

21:36.920 --> 21:37.750
Sew another one?

21:37.750 --> 21:38.750
No, no, no.

21:39.070 --> 21:41.400
Sew two more pockets

21:41.550 --> 21:42.610
inside the jacket.

21:43.160 --> 21:44.360
We won't be so unlucky

21:44.550 --> 21:46.750
that a thief steals everything at once.

21:47.160 --> 21:48.110
That's true.

21:49.030 --> 21:50.240
You are so smart, Xiaolan.

21:50.240 --> 21:50.750
Okay.

21:50.960 --> 21:51.560
All right.

21:53.510 --> 21:54.350
The jacket.

21:54.510 --> 21:55.350
Okay, okay.

21:56.400 --> 21:58.110
It's been 4 or 5 days.

21:58.920 --> 22:01.250
Why haven't the exam results come out yet?

22:02.750 --> 22:04.720
I wonder when Zhou Cheng will arrive.

22:04.720 --> 22:05.880
If he misses me,

22:06.400 --> 22:08.130
then we are just not meant to be.

22:14.960 --> 22:15.960
Comrade Xiaolan!

22:17.830 --> 22:19.230
Did you get the telegram?

22:21.200 --> 22:21.750
I did.

22:27.080 --> 22:32.300
[Capital, Haidian District, Capital Normal University, Xia Ziyu]
[Mother and daughter moved away; detained after refusing to move out; Lan took an exam]

22:29.110 --> 22:29.970
Taking an exam?

22:30.720 --> 22:32.050
College entrance exam?

22:33.110 --> 22:34.030
Don't tell me she hasn't

22:34.030 --> 22:34.920
given up on Wang Jianhua yet?

22:34.920 --> 22:35.450
Jianhua.

22:35.550 --> 22:36.750
You have to come
to the match this afternoon.

22:36.750 --> 22:38.680
Exactly. We can't win without you.

22:39.030 --> 22:39.920
Isn't that Xia Ziyu?

22:39.920 --> 22:40.980
Let's go eat first.

22:41.400 --> 22:42.310
Let's not disturb them.

22:42.310 --> 22:42.960
Let's go.

22:47.070 --> 22:48.200
My class ended late.

22:48.310 --> 22:49.680
You could have started eating.

22:49.680 --> 22:50.720
You didn't have to wait for me.

22:50.720 --> 22:51.780
I didn't wait long.

22:52.000 --> 22:54.160
Besides, we are boyfriend and girlfriend.

22:54.160 --> 22:55.400
If I don't care about you,

22:55.400 --> 22:56.930
who else would I care about?

22:58.550 --> 22:59.150
Let's eat.

22:59.440 --> 23:00.110
Okay.

23:03.720 --> 23:04.110
Here.

23:04.550 --> 23:05.110
Thanks.

23:13.440 --> 23:15.350
You gave me all the braised pork again.

23:15.350 --> 23:16.720
You should have some too.

23:16.720 --> 23:18.590
You're a man. You burn more energy.

23:18.590 --> 23:19.390
Eat more meat.

23:19.550 --> 23:20.030
No, you eat some too.

23:20.030 --> 23:20.550
I'm fine with just vegetables.

23:20.550 --> 23:21.110
Have some.

23:21.110 --> 23:22.240
No need. Really.

23:22.240 --> 23:24.240
If you don't eat, I won't eat either.

23:24.680 --> 23:25.480
Be good. Here.

23:26.270 --> 23:28.200
Eat more.

23:30.070 --> 23:30.590
Eat.

23:33.480 --> 23:34.410
Thank you, Ziyu.

23:35.440 --> 23:36.480
It's nothing.

23:38.070 --> 23:39.640
The money you gave me before

23:39.880 --> 23:41.080
really helped me out.

23:41.400 --> 23:42.400
My dad will soon be

23:42.400 --> 23:44.000
reinstated in the education department.

23:44.000 --> 23:44.640
Really?

23:44.960 --> 23:45.760
That's great!

23:46.110 --> 23:48.030
So I really want to thank you,

23:48.030 --> 23:48.510
Ziyu.

23:50.960 --> 23:52.420
You don't need to thank me.

23:52.440 --> 23:54.070
Your family is my family.

23:57.200 --> 23:57.800
Let's eat.

24:11.160 --> 24:12.590
The self-defense item
I gave you last time,

24:12.590 --> 24:13.520
did you bring it?

24:14.240 --> 24:15.170
It's right here.

24:16.450 --> 24:18.050
I just wanted to come see you.

24:18.200 --> 24:18.640
But I didn't expect

24:18.640 --> 24:19.920
your business to grow so big

24:19.920 --> 24:21.480
that you're going to Longcheng for stock.

24:21.480 --> 24:22.610
Why the sudden rush?

24:23.480 --> 24:24.200
Because I plan to

24:24.200 --> 24:25.550
take the college entrance exam next year.

24:25.550 --> 24:27.030
So I want to pave the way first.

24:27.030 --> 24:27.880
Then I can hand the business to my mom

24:27.880 --> 24:29.210
and focus on my studies.

24:30.110 --> 24:31.440
College entrance exam?

24:32.350 --> 24:33.440
Why did you suddenly think of

24:33.440 --> 24:34.270
going to college?

24:34.270 --> 24:35.590
In this era,

24:35.590 --> 24:36.310
isn't going to college

24:36.310 --> 24:37.640
the natural thing to do?

24:38.270 --> 24:40.200
Stop being lazy to stop being poor,

24:40.400 --> 24:41.270
rely on yourself,

24:41.270 --> 24:42.240
work hard,

24:42.440 --> 24:43.680
and knowledge can change your life.

24:43.680 --> 24:44.440
Isn't that what's written

24:44.440 --> 24:45.270
on the slogans?

24:45.270 --> 24:46.730
Shouldn't I believe them?

24:48.960 --> 24:49.620
You should.

24:50.160 --> 24:51.360
Of course you should.

24:51.960 --> 24:52.960
Comrade Xiaolan.

24:53.240 --> 24:54.370
Every time I see you,

24:54.750 --> 24:55.680
you surprise me.

24:56.400 --> 24:57.550
Now I know

24:58.110 --> 25:00.040
what the difference is between us.

25:00.060 --> 25:01.130
It's courage

25:01.510 --> 25:02.640
and determination.

25:04.070 --> 25:05.200
It's more than that.

25:05.720 --> 25:07.310
There's also a gap of over 40 years

25:07.310 --> 25:09.370
and over 10 years of life experience.

25:10.510 --> 25:11.510
Comrade Xiaolan.

25:12.110 --> 25:13.070
Actually,

25:14.590 --> 25:15.400
it's been 3 months

25:15.400 --> 25:17.000
since I graduated high school.

25:17.000 --> 25:18.400
My family arranged

25:18.550 --> 25:19.880
a pretty good job for me.

25:20.350 --> 25:22.240
I should have reported for duty long ago,

25:22.240 --> 25:23.500
but I haven't gone yet.

25:25.310 --> 25:26.240
I can't quite say

25:27.030 --> 25:28.640
what exactly I'm hesitating about.

25:28.640 --> 25:29.550
You are hesitating

25:29.550 --> 25:31.110
because both
taking the college entrance exam

25:31.110 --> 25:32.040
and going to work

25:32.400 --> 25:33.960
are good options for you.

25:34.310 --> 25:36.030
In fact, taking the exam might look like

25:36.030 --> 25:37.110
taking a detour.

25:37.830 --> 25:39.240
You were going to work anyway.

25:39.240 --> 25:40.960
You'd have a good job without the exam,

25:40.960 --> 25:42.270
so why take the detour?

25:42.590 --> 25:44.110
But I'm different from you.

25:44.110 --> 25:45.440
If I don't take the exam,

25:45.440 --> 25:47.500
I can see the end of my life at a glance.

25:47.640 --> 25:48.500
I don't believe

25:48.590 --> 25:50.450
that I'm stuck like this forever.

25:50.510 --> 25:51.200
So,

25:51.440 --> 25:52.310
no matter how hard the exam is,

25:52.310 --> 25:53.200
I will try.

25:53.750 --> 25:54.350
Of course,

25:54.720 --> 25:56.720
I don't think it's hard for me.

26:00.960 --> 26:01.350
I...

26:01.750 --> 26:03.240
I haven't thought about it

26:03.510 --> 26:04.440
from this angle.

26:05.000 --> 26:06.000
Comrade Xiaolan,

26:06.400 --> 26:07.600
your words woke me up.

26:08.350 --> 26:09.080
In that case,

26:09.310 --> 26:10.170
after I go back,

26:10.550 --> 26:12.280
I will also seriously consider

26:12.400 --> 26:13.550
taking the college entrance exam.

26:13.550 --> 26:14.110
Oh no,

26:14.640 --> 26:15.970
I talked too much again.

26:16.400 --> 26:18.110
Being middle-aged really makes one

26:18.110 --> 26:19.440
love to lecture others.

26:21.830 --> 26:23.110
Whether you take the exam or not

26:23.110 --> 26:24.350
has nothing to do with me.

26:24.350 --> 26:25.750
I was just talking casually.

26:25.750 --> 26:26.880
I didn't give you advice,

26:26.880 --> 26:28.000
nor did I make any promises.

26:28.000 --> 26:29.130
Don't pin this on me.

26:32.400 --> 26:33.160
I do like you,

26:33.640 --> 26:34.400
but I don't need to

26:34.400 --> 26:36.060
gamble with my future, right?

26:37.310 --> 26:38.770
Don't feel too pressured.

26:40.270 --> 26:41.070
I swear to you,

26:41.440 --> 26:42.920
before you finish the exam,

26:42.920 --> 26:44.000
I won't bring up

26:44.000 --> 26:44.800
dating again.

26:46.070 --> 26:46.670
Of course,

26:47.400 --> 26:48.270
if

26:49.240 --> 26:50.240
one day I can catch up with

26:50.240 --> 26:51.160
your pace,

26:52.350 --> 26:53.950
then I hope you can seriously

26:55.000 --> 26:55.880
consider me.

27:01.480 --> 27:02.080
It's done?

27:02.160 --> 27:03.020
I exchanged it.

27:03.200 --> 27:04.200
A sleeper ticket.

27:08.050 --> 27:10.110
Sleeper tickets are hard to get, right?

27:10.110 --> 27:11.590
I didn't really need one—

27:11.590 --> 27:12.590
Comrade Xiaolan,

27:13.070 --> 27:14.200
I know you are smart.

27:14.750 --> 27:16.410
But for a young female comrade

27:16.440 --> 27:17.440
traveling away from home,

27:17.440 --> 27:19.040
one can never be too careful.

27:19.070 --> 27:20.240
From Shangdu to Longcheng,

27:20.240 --> 27:21.900
the train takes over 30 hours.

27:22.480 --> 27:23.480
And this time,

27:23.790 --> 27:25.350
I have things to wrap up too.

27:26.310 --> 27:28.030
I probably can't keep you company.

27:28.030 --> 27:28.590
So do not refuse

27:28.590 --> 27:29.790
this sleeper ticket.

27:30.310 --> 27:31.310
When you're away from home,

27:31.310 --> 27:32.270
safety comes first.

27:32.270 --> 27:33.440
It's not just for me,

27:34.440 --> 27:35.840
but also for your family.

27:36.750 --> 27:38.680
Attention, passengers.

27:38.880 --> 27:40.110
The train to Longcheng,

27:40.110 --> 27:41.480
No. 765,

27:41.640 --> 27:43.000
is now boarding.

27:43.270 --> 27:45.510
Please take your luggage

27:46.000 --> 27:47.250
and line up for ticket check.

27:47.250 --> 27:48.450
Give it to me. Thanks.

27:58.110 --> 27:58.840
Xia Xiaolan!

28:04.350 --> 28:05.000
Stay safe.

28:06.590 --> 28:07.070
Okay.

28:08.880 --> 28:09.410
Goodbye.

28:19.270 --> 28:20.700
From waking up in this spacetime

28:20.700 --> 28:22.160
to taking this step today,

28:22.310 --> 28:23.640
it's been only a month.

28:24.270 --> 28:25.240
My decisiveness

28:25.350 --> 28:26.350
and swift actions

28:26.920 --> 28:28.590
surprised not only those around me,

28:28.590 --> 28:29.720
but even myself.

28:30.590 --> 28:32.240
If the me from the original spacetime

28:32.240 --> 28:33.310
had such

28:33.310 --> 28:34.110
drive,

28:34.350 --> 28:36.160
would everything be different?

28:36.680 --> 28:38.070
Dear passengers,

28:38.240 --> 28:39.640
you are on

28:39.640 --> 28:40.880
the train to Longcheng,

28:40.880 --> 28:42.350
No. 765.

28:42.510 --> 28:45.400
We will pass through Xuxian, Xinyang,

28:45.640 --> 28:48.400
Changzhou, Yuezhou, and Changzhou.

28:48.750 --> 28:50.640
The next stop is Yuezhou.

28:50.640 --> 28:52.310
Yuezhou in this spacetime...

28:52.400 --> 28:53.750
Comrade, here is your meal.

28:53.750 --> 28:54.810
All right. Thanks.

28:59.920 --> 29:00.550
Comrade,

29:00.680 --> 29:02.070
would you like to order a meal?

29:02.070 --> 29:03.400
I'd like a cup of coffee.

29:03.750 --> 29:04.680
What?

29:06.590 --> 29:07.790
What do you have?

29:08.680 --> 29:09.680
Pork with peppers, 20 cents.

29:09.680 --> 29:10.680
Shredded potatoes, 10 cents.

29:10.680 --> 29:12.010
Braised fish, 50 cents.

29:12.240 --> 29:13.510
Pork with peppers, please. Thanks.

29:13.510 --> 29:13.920
Okay.

29:24.200 --> 29:24.750
Sister,

29:25.350 --> 29:26.410
you look educated.

29:28.030 --> 29:29.490
Traveling alone by train?

29:30.590 --> 29:31.850
Where are you heading?

29:32.110 --> 29:32.910
To Longcheng.

29:33.790 --> 29:34.790
Looking for a job?

29:35.790 --> 29:37.320
What kind of job do you want?

29:39.200 --> 29:39.650
[English]

29:40.790 --> 29:42.650
I want to do live streaming sales.

29:43.920 --> 29:45.180
Do you think I can do it?

29:45.750 --> 29:46.440
Sure.

29:47.160 --> 29:48.750
Any job you want is fine.

29:48.990 --> 29:50.350
I have connections.

29:50.550 --> 29:51.480
Leave it to me.

29:53.000 --> 29:53.920
Did you bring your letter of introduction?

29:53.920 --> 29:54.650
Let me see it.

29:55.790 --> 29:56.720
Like hell I will.

29:57.070 --> 29:58.470
What would I do with that?

29:58.640 --> 29:59.350
If I give you the letter,

29:59.350 --> 30:00.350
I'd have to give myself to you too, right?

30:00.350 --> 30:01.160
Crazy.

30:01.550 --> 30:03.720
What are you saying? I don't understand.

30:03.720 --> 30:04.920
Stop pretending.

30:06.000 --> 30:07.030
You're a human trafficker, aren't you?

30:07.030 --> 30:08.560
That trick won't work on me.

30:08.720 --> 30:09.960
Don't talk nonsense.

30:10.200 --> 30:11.440
If you don't want help, fine.

30:11.440 --> 30:13.030
You're treating my kindness like dirt.

30:13.030 --> 30:15.160
Trying to switch cars
to trick another lady?

30:15.160 --> 30:16.510
Everyone, be careful.

30:16.790 --> 30:18.440
This person is a human trafficker.

30:18.440 --> 30:19.000
Don't be—

30:19.000 --> 30:19.790
You're talking nonsense!

30:19.790 --> 30:21.110
Who are you calling a human trafficker?

30:21.110 --> 30:22.680
How can you make false accusations
when you're a kid yourself?

30:22.680 --> 30:23.830
You're terrible!

30:24.400 --> 30:25.370
I've heard that

30:25.680 --> 30:26.920
there are traffickers on trains now

30:26.920 --> 30:27.680
who steal children

30:27.680 --> 30:28.880
and trick women.

30:29.350 --> 30:30.160
When they see

30:30.160 --> 30:31.310
young women,

30:31.510 --> 30:33.030
they'd say they can bring them down south
to make big money.

30:33.030 --> 30:33.590
But in the end—

30:33.590 --> 30:34.510
All right, shut up!

30:34.510 --> 30:34.960
It's none of your business.

30:34.960 --> 30:35.240
Bro.

30:35.240 --> 30:37.300
There aren't that many traffickers.

30:37.790 --> 30:38.440
Yeah.

30:38.440 --> 30:39.700
This girl looks young.

30:39.790 --> 30:40.680
It's probably a misunderstanding.

30:40.680 --> 30:41.310
Let's just eat.

30:41.310 --> 30:42.160
A misunderstanding?

30:42.160 --> 30:44.400
You two are in on it together, aren't you?

30:44.400 --> 30:46.070
I think you're the one with the problem.

30:46.070 --> 30:47.160
Do you even have ID?

30:47.160 --> 30:47.790
Come on, let me see.

30:47.790 --> 30:48.750
Go away. Don't bother me.

30:48.750 --> 30:49.400
Where's your letter of introduction?

30:49.400 --> 30:49.920
Let go of me.

30:49.920 --> 30:50.920
Introduction...

30:51.030 --> 30:52.030
You're stealing my bag!

30:52.030 --> 30:53.000
What's going on? What's going on?

30:53.000 --> 30:53.800
Stop arguing.

30:54.590 --> 30:55.720
Behave yourselves!

30:56.920 --> 30:57.850
What's going on?

30:59.310 --> 31:00.000
Officer.

31:00.790 --> 31:01.750
This young lady

31:01.750 --> 31:03.070
was reading here.

31:03.680 --> 31:04.480
And this woman

31:04.480 --> 31:05.590
came over to chat her up.

31:05.590 --> 31:06.390
The two of them

31:06.480 --> 31:07.610
got into a conflict.

31:07.870 --> 31:09.270
I think for safety reasons,

31:09.270 --> 31:10.400
could you please check

31:10.400 --> 31:11.070
their IDs?

31:12.510 --> 31:13.550
Take out your IDs,

31:13.880 --> 31:14.410
tickets,

31:14.480 --> 31:16.200
and letters of introduction.

31:29.590 --> 31:30.320
Xia Xiaolan.

31:31.000 --> 31:31.440
Yes.

31:31.750 --> 31:32.720
Going to Longcheng.

31:32.720 --> 31:33.160
Right.

31:35.160 --> 31:35.640
Yours.

31:45.270 --> 31:46.470
Where's your letter?

31:46.510 --> 31:47.110
I-It's...

31:47.270 --> 31:49.350
in my luggage in the carriage.

31:49.750 --> 31:50.550
Bring it here.

31:52.590 --> 31:53.830
Go. I'll go with you.

32:03.750 --> 32:04.510
S-Sir.

32:07.480 --> 32:08.740
Thank you for earlier.

32:09.030 --> 32:09.680
You're welcome.

32:09.680 --> 32:10.480
When you're away from home,

32:10.480 --> 32:12.140
you really should be careful.

32:14.160 --> 32:15.440
You're just a little girl,

32:15.440 --> 32:16.840
but you've got some guts.

32:27.040 --> 32:28.070
Your pork and pepper rice.

32:28.070 --> 32:28.550
Thanks.

32:37.790 --> 32:38.920
Just you wait.

32:39.880 --> 32:41.240
You two useless idiots.

32:42.440 --> 32:46.470
[Yuezhou Station]

32:52.310 --> 32:53.310
I've long thought

32:53.550 --> 32:54.830
that in my old hometown

32:54.830 --> 32:57.160
there might be clues
about my time travel.

32:57.640 --> 33:00.240
But when I finally
saved enough for the ticket,

33:00.480 --> 33:01.480
I got cold feet.

33:04.070 --> 33:05.270
This coincidence

33:05.270 --> 33:06.400
getting off here

33:07.240 --> 33:09.550
might be destiny.

33:09.550 --> 33:10.030
Right?

33:10.200 --> 33:10.790
Why don't we pick

33:10.790 --> 33:12.030
some nice floral fabric first.

33:12.030 --> 33:12.960
Yeah, I think so too.

33:12.960 --> 33:13.560
Excuse me.

33:13.880 --> 33:14.880
I'd like to ask

33:15.240 --> 33:16.200
if you know

33:16.270 --> 33:17.530
someone named Liu Mei?

33:17.550 --> 33:19.350
She is a salesperson
at the winery's sales workshop.

33:19.350 --> 33:20.210
A salesperson?

33:20.920 --> 33:21.520
Xiao Song,

33:21.920 --> 33:23.590
is there a Liu Mei in your workshop?

33:23.590 --> 33:24.920
There's no such person.

33:25.160 --> 33:25.890
There isn't?

33:25.960 --> 33:27.680
Could you please think again?

33:27.920 --> 33:28.790
Think about what?

33:28.790 --> 33:30.680
There are only 5 of us in sales.

33:30.790 --> 33:32.190
I'd know if there was one.

33:33.400 --> 33:34.070
Thanks.

33:34.830 --> 33:35.590
Wang.

33:56.740 --> 33:59.920
My mom wouldn't paste
the "Happiness" character upside down.

33:59.920 --> 34:00.410
Hello.

34:00.830 --> 34:01.960
Who are you looking for?

34:01.960 --> 34:02.480
Hi.

34:03.080 --> 34:05.000
Does Xia Weimin
from Brewing Workshop No.4

34:05.000 --> 34:05.830
live here?

34:06.200 --> 34:07.200
You've got the wrong building.

34:07.200 --> 34:09.460
There's no one surnamed Xia in this yard.

34:09.960 --> 34:10.510
Dajuan,

34:10.840 --> 34:12.150
call Chaoying back for dinner.

34:12.150 --> 34:12.630
Okay!

34:13.219 --> 34:13.820
Chaoying,

34:14.000 --> 34:15.190
come home for dinner!

34:15.190 --> 34:15.590
Okay!

34:15.590 --> 34:16.790
Your dad made dinner.

34:18.800 --> 34:19.670
Hello, Miss!

34:45.630 --> 34:46.280
Xiaolan!

34:47.440 --> 34:48.239
What's wrong?

34:49.320 --> 34:50.050
Are you hurt?

34:50.250 --> 34:50.800
Get up.

34:50.800 --> 34:51.190
What happened?

34:51.190 --> 34:52.320
Let me see if you're hurt.

34:52.320 --> 34:53.050
Does it hurt?

34:53.070 --> 34:53.590
Don't cry.

34:53.590 --> 34:54.850
Did you drop your ball?

34:55.480 --> 34:57.080
There, there. Let's go home.

34:57.990 --> 34:58.870
Xiaolan, look.

34:59.150 --> 34:59.670
Catch!

35:01.000 --> 35:02.460
Kick it to Mommy, Xiaolan.

35:19.960 --> 35:21.190
This spacetime

35:21.440 --> 35:23.110
is exactly as I remember it.

35:24.440 --> 35:25.440
The difference is

35:25.920 --> 35:27.250
my parents aren't here,

35:28.070 --> 35:30.070
so the future me won't exist either.

35:31.320 --> 35:32.430
But I clearly carry

35:32.430 --> 35:33.800
memories of the past,

35:34.190 --> 35:36.000
and I was truly here.

35:37.190 --> 35:38.920
How do I describe this feeling?

35:40.550 --> 35:42.280
Homeless, rootless,

35:42.920 --> 35:43.800
with no ties—

35:44.400 --> 35:45.860
a completely fresh start.

35:47.760 --> 35:48.920
It's like a game,

35:49.400 --> 35:51.030
and I'm an experienced player

35:51.030 --> 35:52.690
who just opened a new account.

35:57.070 --> 35:59.190
Since I don't exist in this spacetime,

35:59.190 --> 36:00.250
then, Xia Xiaolan,

36:01.440 --> 36:02.710
I'm going to change our destiny

36:02.710 --> 36:03.760
and defy the odds.

36:42.490 --> 36:46.700
[Longcheng Train Station]

36:49.320 --> 36:50.150
Need a ride?

36:51.070 --> 36:51.930
Do you need one?

37:03.230 --> 37:04.550
Miss, need a ride?

37:04.550 --> 37:05.510
My car is brand new.

37:05.510 --> 37:06.360
No, thanks.

37:07.230 --> 37:08.110
Hey, beautiful.

37:08.110 --> 37:08.800
It's free.

37:08.800 --> 37:10.110
I'll take you wherever you want.

37:10.110 --> 37:10.770
No, thanks.

37:11.440 --> 37:11.840
Beautiful.

37:11.840 --> 37:13.070
It's dangerous to be alone.

37:13.070 --> 37:13.550
Come on.

37:13.550 --> 37:14.000
Let me give you a ride.

37:14.000 --> 37:15.230
I said no. Move.

37:15.880 --> 37:17.280
It's dangerous for you to be alone.

37:17.280 --> 37:17.920
Move!

37:19.880 --> 37:21.000
Little girl, you're pretty tough.

37:21.000 --> 37:22.280
Pretty girl, you're very tough.

37:22.280 --> 37:23.340
Where are you from?

37:34.440 --> 37:35.090
Bai.

37:35.320 --> 37:36.650
You injured my brother.

37:36.670 --> 37:37.150
Pay up.

37:37.280 --> 37:38.460
You have to pay.

37:38.920 --> 37:40.190
I'll pay you with a coffin.

37:40.190 --> 37:41.150
Do you want it?

37:42.000 --> 37:43.800
You might as well be dead.

37:44.230 --> 37:45.330
Screw off!

37:50.590 --> 37:51.230
Pretty lady,

37:51.230 --> 37:51.960
are you okay?

37:52.230 --> 37:52.760
I'm fine.

37:52.880 --> 37:53.410
Let's go.

37:53.710 --> 37:54.110
Okay.

38:14.960 --> 38:15.560
Mr. Huang,

38:15.780 --> 38:16.360
two bottles.

38:16.360 --> 38:17.360
-I'll pay.
-Okay.

38:20.190 --> 38:21.440
Have a soda. Cool off.

38:23.630 --> 38:24.760
Thanks for earlier.

38:24.840 --> 38:25.800
What should I call you?

38:25.800 --> 38:26.710
My surname is Bai.

38:26.710 --> 38:27.800
My name is Bai Zhenzhu.

38:27.800 --> 38:28.320
I run

38:28.630 --> 38:30.160
the fruit stall over there.

38:31.360 --> 38:32.750
You seem older than me.

38:32.880 --> 38:33.760
How about I call you

38:33.760 --> 38:34.360
Sis Bai?

38:34.810 --> 38:35.520
Sure.

38:35.550 --> 38:36.550
Call me whatever you want.

38:36.550 --> 38:37.750
You have great moves.

38:39.150 --> 38:41.230
My family
used to run a martial arts school.

38:41.230 --> 38:42.880
No one learns martial arts now.

38:42.880 --> 38:44.800
My fellow disciples
have all changed careers.

38:44.800 --> 38:46.320
Those guys just now

38:46.440 --> 38:47.880
have been here for months,

38:47.880 --> 38:49.210
making a mess of things.

38:49.230 --> 38:51.150
I can't handle every petty theft.

38:51.670 --> 38:53.000
But seeing you about to be kidnapped

38:53.000 --> 38:54.070
in public today,

38:54.070 --> 38:54.960
I had to step in.

38:55.150 --> 38:56.510
Even though
the Bai Martial Arts School is gone,

38:56.510 --> 38:58.000
we can't lose our sense of honor.

38:58.000 --> 38:59.190
From your accent,

38:59.190 --> 39:00.250
you're not a local.

39:00.320 --> 39:02.280
Why did you come to Longcheng alone?

39:02.280 --> 39:02.760
No,

39:02.760 --> 39:03.760
I came with a friend.

39:03.760 --> 39:04.890
She'll be here soon.

39:05.400 --> 39:06.320
I'll wait with you.

39:06.320 --> 39:06.960
No need.

39:07.190 --> 39:08.190
I won't keep you from your business.

39:08.190 --> 39:09.120
Please go ahead.

39:09.830 --> 39:11.120
Find me if you need anything.

39:11.120 --> 39:12.190
My stall is right over there.

39:12.190 --> 39:12.850
Okay, sure.

39:13.150 --> 39:13.800
Thanks.

39:31.360 --> 39:32.430
I've heard

39:32.430 --> 39:34.070
the clothing market in the 80s

39:34.070 --> 39:35.270
was like a wet market.

39:35.800 --> 39:36.480
It's true.

39:53.150 --> 39:54.150
Okay, thanks.

39:54.840 --> 39:55.970
Come and take a look!

39:56.710 --> 39:57.320
Come on!

39:57.920 --> 39:59.720
Everything over there is 5 yuan!

39:59.760 --> 40:00.960
Sir, how much is this?

40:01.360 --> 40:02.890
This one? Wholesale for 13.

40:03.000 --> 40:04.230
Retail for 16.

40:04.510 --> 40:05.550
Others sell it for 8.

40:05.550 --> 40:06.510
Yours is too expensive.

40:06.510 --> 40:08.000
Look at this fabric.

40:08.030 --> 40:09.230
How can my clothes

40:09.230 --> 40:10.760
compare to that cheap junk?

40:11.250 --> 40:12.440
Where are you selling them?

40:12.440 --> 40:13.630
It's not cheap here.

40:13.800 --> 40:15.710
Be careful not to lose money.

40:16.110 --> 40:16.960
To Yunan.

40:17.230 --> 40:18.230
Yunan?

40:19.960 --> 40:21.400
For Yunan, pick from over there.

40:21.400 --> 40:22.110
Those over there are cheaper.

40:22.110 --> 40:22.550
No, no.

40:22.630 --> 40:23.920
We people in Yunan also need to wear

40:23.920 --> 40:25.650
the most fashionable clothes.

40:25.670 --> 40:26.400
Fair enough.

40:26.760 --> 40:28.290
But let me be clear upfront.

40:28.360 --> 40:29.960
If you can't sell them,

40:29.960 --> 40:31.320
I don't accept returns here.

40:31.320 --> 40:32.430
The styles are all here.

40:32.430 --> 40:33.630
Pick whatever you like.

40:33.630 --> 40:34.110
Okay.

40:35.360 --> 40:35.960
By the way,

40:36.190 --> 40:37.630
since you're selling in Yunan,

40:37.630 --> 40:38.840
you surely won't have time
to come here often.

40:38.840 --> 40:39.760
When you can't make it,

40:39.760 --> 40:40.920
call the number on there to contact me

40:40.920 --> 40:41.590
to place an order.

40:41.590 --> 40:42.280
Okay, thanks.

40:42.280 --> 40:43.440
Okay, take your time.

40:43.440 --> 40:44.640
Sir, how much is this?

40:44.880 --> 40:45.810
Coming, coming!

40:46.190 --> 40:47.440
Everything is 5 yuan!

40:47.550 --> 40:49.070
Wholesale here is also 5 yuan.

40:49.070 --> 40:50.440
Retail is also 5 yuan.

40:51.670 --> 40:52.510
Just 5 yuan.

40:52.630 --> 40:53.710
That's the rock-bottom price, okay?

40:53.710 --> 40:54.840
Rock-bottom price.

41:01.110 --> 41:02.710
She really is a fruit seller.

41:03.190 --> 41:04.800
Seems I was too guarded.

41:06.710 --> 41:08.510
I still need to return the favor.

41:08.630 --> 41:10.320
Cheap and good!

41:12.590 --> 41:13.320
Ma'am, what—

41:14.190 --> 41:15.130
Pretty girl!

41:15.230 --> 41:16.230
It's you!

41:16.580 --> 41:18.220
Sis Bai, I'm Xia Xiaolan.

41:18.250 --> 41:19.360
Just call me Xiaolan.

41:19.360 --> 41:20.480
Xia Xiaolan.

41:20.800 --> 41:21.730
Hello, Xiaolan.

41:22.480 --> 41:24.070
Are you done with your business?

41:24.070 --> 41:25.470
Where's your companion?

41:26.190 --> 41:27.840
She got her goods

41:27.840 --> 41:29.170
and took the train back.

41:29.960 --> 41:31.400
Our Longcheng longans

41:31.510 --> 41:32.400
are delicious.

41:32.660 --> 41:33.510
Here, try some.

41:33.510 --> 41:34.030
Thanks.

41:38.010 --> 41:38.920
Longans from 1983

41:38.920 --> 41:39.670
are so sweet?

41:39.800 --> 41:40.670
If you like them,

41:40.670 --> 41:42.000
I'll give you some more.

41:42.800 --> 41:43.760
No need, really.

41:43.760 --> 41:44.280
That's enough.

41:44.280 --> 41:45.590
-It's okay.
-It's too troublesome.

41:45.590 --> 41:46.410
It's no trouble.

41:46.410 --> 41:47.550
I'm just idling anyway.

41:47.550 --> 41:48.760
There's no business right now.

41:48.760 --> 41:49.110
I...

41:49.480 --> 41:51.010
Take these to eat on the way.

41:51.590 --> 41:52.070
Okay.

41:52.440 --> 41:54.640
I can't just eat here and take some to go.

41:56.110 --> 41:57.160
This piece of clothing,

41:57.160 --> 41:58.190
you should take it.

41:58.190 --> 41:59.540
Thanks for saving me just now.

41:59.540 --> 41:59.950
Here.

42:00.030 --> 42:01.190
Put it away, quick.

42:01.320 --> 42:02.150
No, no, no.

42:02.170 --> 42:03.110
I can't, I can't.

42:03.360 --> 42:04.320
Put it away.

42:05.840 --> 42:06.920
I just saw injustice

42:06.920 --> 42:07.940
and stepped in to help.

42:07.940 --> 42:09.010
If I take your stuff,

42:09.010 --> 42:10.340
what would that make me?

42:10.720 --> 42:11.440
When you go back,

42:11.440 --> 42:13.190
you still need these to make money.

42:13.190 --> 42:14.590
It's not easy for anyone.

42:15.320 --> 42:15.710
Okay.

42:15.840 --> 42:16.640
Then thank you

42:16.880 --> 42:17.590
for this.

42:19.320 --> 42:19.920
Sis Bai,

42:20.510 --> 42:21.840
have you ever thought of

42:22.230 --> 42:24.360
setting up your stall somewhere else?

42:26.040 --> 42:27.520
Business was okay

42:27.550 --> 42:28.810
in my previous spot.

42:29.200 --> 42:30.040
But later,

42:30.070 --> 42:31.920
a junior of mine got married,

42:32.030 --> 42:33.760
so I gave the stall to the couple

42:34.000 --> 42:35.860
and found another one for myself.

42:36.190 --> 42:38.190
This place really isn't working out.

42:38.190 --> 42:39.070
Then,

42:39.440 --> 42:40.960
have you thought about switching trades?

42:40.960 --> 42:41.840
I have!

42:42.400 --> 42:44.060
I went to the clothing market.

42:44.320 --> 42:45.800
Those bell-bottoms,

42:45.800 --> 42:46.590
skinny jeans...

42:46.590 --> 42:48.110
They make my head spin.

42:48.110 --> 42:49.070
I don't get them.

42:49.480 --> 42:50.670
It's all just to look pretty in,

42:50.670 --> 42:51.730
but hard to work in.

42:52.720 --> 42:54.040
You're right, Sis Bai.

42:54.070 --> 42:55.150
But in the future,

42:55.170 --> 42:56.280
people will be increasingly

42:56.280 --> 42:58.360
willing to pay for things just for show.

42:58.360 --> 43:00.070
You can predict the future?
